00:11:45.059 --> 00:11:50.500
Above all, we do this because we want to please God and to be his friend.

00:11:50.899 --> 00:11:56.899
So then how can you develop a friendship with God, show initiative, and put forth the effort?

00:11:57.700 --> 00:12:07.700
