Witnesses, he was followed. Some former associates even attended a few meetings, so as to understand

00:26:49.390 --> 00:26:55.150
what brought about such a great change in Jose. But once they were satisfied that he was not a

00:26:55.150 --> 00:27:02.509
danger to them, they left him alone. At age 17, Jose was baptized as one of Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:27:03.230 --> 00:27:10.269
As God's friend, Jose soon started sharing what he was learning full time. Instead of scheming to

00:27:10.269 --> 00:27:17.710
kill people, he could now share a message of love and of hope with them. What a great reward

00:27:17.710 --> 00:27:24.750
for choosing to become Jehovah's Friend. Yes, even those who were once enemies can learn to be at

00:27:24.750 --> 00:27:32.990
peace with one another and be God's friends. So what have we learned? We have reviewed why friendship

00:27:32.990 --> 00:27:40.750
with God is realistic and possible for us. The Bible tells us that since ancient times, God has

00:27:40.750 --> 00:27:47.630
called some humans his friends. We also looked at what God has done to heal the breach or close the

00:27:47.630 --> 00:27:56.509
gap between us and him. How has he done so? By means of his Son. Through Jesus, Jehovah God

00:27:56.509 --> 00:28:03.309
provided the ransom sacrifice that was needed to redeem us from sin. Then we looked at what you

00:28:03.309 --> 00:28:09.390
must do to take advantage of God's mercy and become his friend. This includes studying his word

00:28:09.390 --> 00:28:17.869
the Bible and then imitating his outstanding qualities. Finally, we considered how you can find a

00:28:17.869 --> 00:28:26.509
meaningful life now as well as true peace with others. Jehovah promises that his friends will

00:28:26.509 --> 00:28:35.630
receive eternal life in peace. If that is what you yearn for, then please accept our invitation to

00:28:36.269 --> 00:28:44.109
study the Bible with Jehovah's Witnesses. By doing so, you will learn about an unending future when

00:28:44.109 --> 00:28:51.630
anguish of heart is gone forever and an unending future in which God will permanently wipe away

00:28:51.630 --> 00:29:02.029
tears from the faces of his friends. That future is not only possible. It is the future that God promises.
